    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision! While it's currently in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it serves as a fantastic, budget-friendly starting point for a restoration enthusiast. Grab this opportunity to bring a classic back to life at a great price!",
