      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a refined exterior and a cabin preserved with professional care, it delivers a driving experience characterized by mechanical precision and sophisticated comfort. Every component has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and longevity. Invest in a vehicle that balances prestige with proven reliability.",
      "price": 36500.0,
